{"tid":645153,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港第一語音普通話 第二英文 第三先粵","createTime":"2018-04-28T00:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T02:18:04.000Z","uid":2719,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9041446fab5b5cfb308b0800e9520c96ad4d23d8","tid":645153,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T00:39:15.000Z","msg":"中學生傾向寫殘體 <br />\n之前連登先同班中學雞開正殘體戰<br />\n<br />\n打字用普拼<br />\n即係打字嗰時個mindset係普通話<br />\n<br />\n小學雞即時反應用普通話對話<br />\n英文問路片大家都睇到心寒<br />\n個個跟住笑無人屌柒講蝗語嘅蟲<br />\n<br />\n我相信不久將來<br />\n班00後夠歲數從政<br />\n就會爭取(topic)<br />\n<br />\n90後爭取民主自決 真普選<br />\n00後爭取真中國香港<br />\n(Eg大陸網睇劇開放香港ip 淘寶全國免運費包香港)<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdd0d749e7b0dfaa2f92c01bde05743fb7aa25d","tid":645153,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70ac44f799e664de25f7537136803118609e254","tid":645153,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:14:15.000Z","msg":"所以講滿洲話嘅滾返支那去！"},{"pid":"fa72ca211171cc465d0c2aa2ceb6b116eebcaa52","tid":645153,"uid":135767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T02:18:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}